\label{prop: flatness sorites}
Let $f:X\rightarrow Y$ be a morphism of fs log schemes. Then
\begin{enumerate}
\item If $f$ is log smooth, then $f$ is log flat.
\item If $X$ and $Y$ are locally Noetherian fine log schemes and ${f}$
is locally of finite presentation, then if $f$ is log flat and integral,
${f}$ is flat.
\end{enumerate}

